- You know how this works,
better than most.

39:35.170 --> 39:36.831
You don't belong
in this plane.

39:36.940 --> 39:38.465
- I'm not going
back to limbo.

39:38.570 --> 39:41.335
- No, you're not.

39:41.440 --> 39:44.410
- You know what happens when
a death spot is destroyed?

39:46.410 --> 39:48.174
- You say we're linked?
I'll take you with me.

39:48.280 --> 39:51.045
I'll leave you there.
I'll shred you.

39:51.150 --> 39:52.584
You don't know
what I can do.

39:52.690 --> 39:54.488
- Oh no, I do.

39:57.820 --> 39:59.822
Why do you think
I like you so much?

40:13.610 --> 40:17.171
(Exhales)

40:17.280 --> 40:18.748
(Grunting)

40:28.420 --> 40:29.910
(Screaming)

